# Lou32 Deployment Protocol - Application Configuration
# 
# This file defines which applications will be installed via winget.
# Modify this list to customize your deployment.
#
# Format: Name|WingetPackageId|Description
# Lines starting with # are comments and will be ignored.
# To disable an application, comment it out by adding # at the start of the line.

# Version Control
Git|Git.Git|Distributed version control system

